items.title: Renew & Replace License & ID
items.snippet: If you already have an Oklahoma Driver License or State Identification Card ... Bring your current driver's license as your primary form of identification.

metatags.twitter:title: Renew & Replace License & ID
metatags.twitter:description: If you already have an Oklahoma Driver License (DL) or State Identification Card, you can renew or replace it online or in person at a Licensed Operator, or Service Oklahoma Licensing Office.

items.title: Commercial Driving CDL
items.snippet: Oklahoma requires a Commercial Driver's License (CDL). Note: Special endorsements may be required for certain vehicles or cargo.
items.htmlSnippet: Oklahoma requires a Commercial Driver's License (CDL). Note: Special endorsements may be required for certain vehicles or cargo.

metatags.twitter:title: Commercial Driving CDL
metatags.twitter:description: If you plan to operate certain specialized types of vehicles such as buses, heavy oversized vehicles, or vehicles that carry multiple passengers, Oklahoma requires a Commercial Driver's License (CDL) .
